Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,(AV引退 时本杏)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢咖肤呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢咖啡加茶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,第—次在家里装摄影机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.52,0:01:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,希望不会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,0:01:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在家里做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.66,0:01:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不会带男生回家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.67,0:01:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,都是看漫画书
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.54,0:01:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看电視
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这样被拍好羞耻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,早上早起呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,早上是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上也是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一样早睡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,早睡不对吗？我觉得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,几点睡?\N9点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是小孩吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就是习惯早睡早起呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,以后打算会怎样做?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一般的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样的?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就是毕业之后过正常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那样，就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的我也不是很清楚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,很像分手的感觉呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,摄影机前会害差呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,问一下想做什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有打算吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，算是有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这样出外景拍摄次数很多吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没有,很少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很新鲜的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,再見，时本杏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,习慣摄影机之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,然后说开始拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,会很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这次的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不会说开始拍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一直拍着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,天气很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可以开心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,其实阴天也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,当然有太阳是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是会很热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有点云还是比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一次拍摄的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要哭啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是鼻子不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,花粉症呀?\N 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,会难过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,其实还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,都是不认识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而且第一次在很多人面前脫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候，真的很怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是要拍下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但是己经再拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就只好硬着头皮拍完
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:09:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候，真的很羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,太紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,头脑都是一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不紧张吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,男优要上场时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,也会紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,当然工作人员变多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也是很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是唷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就开始尝试口交
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因为要被颜射
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以还被说等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要让精液在脸上的同时说感想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没有想到会这样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,第一年那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,因为都是很多新的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是第2年开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就觉得习惯这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,到第3年开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得有点膩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,还要继续吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真的开始很犹豫这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是唷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是大家的支持吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,以前的男友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有问过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,后来拍摄之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,高中的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候一直很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,后来被说很可爱时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那么吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,从这里有阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,来了\N是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,今天可以开心拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不用想太多那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢被说可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,会说别人可爱吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,到了国中之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就开始变得很成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会想这些呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是会想很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会想吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想尝试看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,才会进来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没有特別想要成为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,说要当偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,其实也还好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢怎样的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,想要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能是因为自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不是想要一直这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:18:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因为做这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,常常需要办活动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要跟别人有互动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我并没有需要这些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,现在生活上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好像都是以这个为主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得很累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很安心的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好远
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,过去那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,现在要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,引退之后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就是新的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这样看很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这些感觉不会体验到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.65,0:21:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,其实要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.69,0:21:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都要体验
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:22:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就不会珍借吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就是要这样说再見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.64,0:22:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,也才会怀念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.71,0:22:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不想要每天做爱吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.57,0:23:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.69,0:24:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,今天要結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.70,0:24:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.70,0:24:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不过还有其他的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.61,0:24:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要开始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.71,0:24:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.57,0:24:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.57,0:24:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.71,0:24:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.56,0:25:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.70,0:25:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我是AV男优
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.70,0:25:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.71,0:25:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,知道你要引退了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.71,0:25:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所以特地来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.58,0:25:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,送你引退的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.59,0:25:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.56,0:25:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是AV男优
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.56,0:25:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.56,0:25:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次見
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.57,0:25:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,还沒有跟他做过爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.58,0:26:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,最后的话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.58,0:26:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里做爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.59,0:26:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他做爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.56,0:26:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多事情想说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.70,0:26:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可以趁这次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.70,0:26:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好好的表达心意
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.56,0:26:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.56,0:26:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很多肌肉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.70,0:26:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.71,0:27:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这样感觉可以
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.58,0:27:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,做很多激烈的运动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.72,0:27:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.72,0:27:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,抱着跑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.69,0:27:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.57,0:27:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,跑去旅馆吧\N 不要呀
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.58,0:27:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样\N 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.64,0:28:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.72,0:28:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那么現在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.59,0:28:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.59,0:28:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.57,0:28:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们現在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.57,0:28:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我要引退
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.71,0:28:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.58,0:28:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要开始AV男优的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.59,0:28:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,请加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.59,0:28:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.57,0:29:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有过这样做爱吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.57,0:29:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,今天会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.58,0:29:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.58,0:29:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,体验看看
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.59,0:29:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.59,0:29:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想性交
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.60,0:29:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.57,0:29:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.58,0:29:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.71,0:29:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.72,0:30:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道时本杏吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.73,0:30:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.57,0:30:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很多种呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.57,0:30:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.71,0:30:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.59,0:30:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,面紙
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.72,0:30:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.59,0:30:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.57,0:30:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.71,0:30:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.58,0:30:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞唷
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.59,0:31:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.60,0:31:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,性交
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.60,0:31:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,想做了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.57,0:31:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要做了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.58,0:31:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.58,0:31:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.63,0:31:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.57,0:31:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,想我怎么玩弄呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.71,0:31:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,流汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.68,0:32:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你脫
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.59,0:32:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.59,0:32:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己脫吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.60,0:32:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.60,0:32:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我该做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.58,0:32:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒\N谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.58,0:32:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒的身材
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.59,0:32:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是唷
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.60,0:32:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.57,0:32:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不要舔腋下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.72,0:33:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以舔腋下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.60,0:33:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.60,0:33:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,再温柔一点
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.71,0:33:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是唷
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.58,0:33:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,请躺下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.73,0:33:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.60,0:33:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不能看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.61,0:34:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.72,0:34:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.73,0:34:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想要什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.74,0:34:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我脫掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.58,0:34:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.72,0:34:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,直接看啰
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.59,0:35:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.73,0:35:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.74,0:35:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,很臭吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.74,0:35:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.72,0:35:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,被人说过这样子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.73,0:36:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有被说过
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.60,0:36:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是唷
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.74,0:36:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候的男优有说
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.65,0:36:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.59,0:36:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我脫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.73,0:36:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.74,0:36:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒问題
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.59,0:37:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.73,0:37:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.60,0:37:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.61,0:37:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好像不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.69,0:37:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这样会不行
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.60,0:37:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.60,0:37:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.61,0:37:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,內裤
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.59,0:38:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.63,0:38:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.60,0:38:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想要你压在脸上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.61,0:38:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好突然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.59,0:38:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.61,0:38:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,想要舔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.58,0:39:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好突然
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.59,0:39:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要溫柔一点
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.73,0:39:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可以舔吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.60,0:39:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.61,0:39:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.69,0:39:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,什么声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.60,0:39:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.60,0:39:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有弄到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.60,0:39:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，有弄到
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.58,0:40:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.72,0:40:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.60,0:40:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.60,0:40:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可以，会痒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.61,0:40:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那我舔了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.63,0:40:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好兴奋呀
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.74,0:41:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒，好湿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.61,0:41:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好突然
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.65,0:41:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.72,0:41:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.60,0:41:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.61,0:41:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.62,0:41:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.59,0:41:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,插入啰
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.59,0:41:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.73,0:42:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,慢一点
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.74,0:42:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.74,0:42:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要插入了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.59,0:42:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,插入了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.74,0:42:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，插入了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.74,0:42:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.64,0:43:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢变快
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.61,0:43:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.61,0:43:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可以脱掉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.62,0:43:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,请脫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.61,0:43:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,很多肌肉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.62,0:44:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.59,0:44:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.74,0:44:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.63,0:45:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.60,0:45:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.68,0:45:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,换体位吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.75,0:45:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可以呀
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.62,0:45:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什么体位?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.62,0:45:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,骑乘位可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.62,0:45:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.60,0:46:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我骑乘位不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.61,0:46:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是唷
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.72,0:46:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,腳拾高吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.62,0:46:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.60,0:46:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.74,0:47:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪唷
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.66,0:47:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,来亲嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.60,0:47:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.61,0:48:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?\N很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.75,0:48:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这样也可以吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.76,0:48:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,换姿勢吧\N 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.76,0:48:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.76,0:48:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.71,0:48:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,想要这样试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.75,0:48:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.60,0:49:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.74,0:49:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,换背后插入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.75,0:49:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.63,0:49:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这样插可以吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.67,0:49:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?\N很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.66,0:50:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.70,0:50:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.74,0:50:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要去啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.74,0:50:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.65,0:50:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.62,0:50:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.60,0:50:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.61,0:50:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,会很舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.62,0:51:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.63,0:51:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子压上来
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.64,0:51:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.61,0:51:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.61,0:51:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要太急
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.60,0:51:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.75,0:51:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.77,0:52:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,有插到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.62,0:52:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.62,0:53:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.70,0:53:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.64,0:53:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.61,0:53:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.75,0:53:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,射了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.76,0:53:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.61,0:54:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒呀
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.75,0:54:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.75,0:54:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.64,0:54:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.64,0:54:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,还可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.75,0:54:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不听话不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.69,0:54:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.77,0:55:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不行
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.77,0:55:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.78,0:55:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.61,0:55:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我是前辈唷
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.75,0:55:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.76,0:55:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.76,0:55:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.63,0:55:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.62,0:55:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.66,0:56:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你还会更厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.67,0:56:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,请加油
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.64,0:56:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.65,0:56:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.62,0:56:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.62,0:56:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.77,0:56:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，时本杏
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.64,0:56:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.65,0:56:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,都会记得你的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.65,0:57:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们换地方吧\N   嗯好
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.76,0:57:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个男优
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.63,0:57:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这次的话
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.67,0:57:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,换上制服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.67,0:57:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,穿制服的设定吗?\N      对的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.66,0:58:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,会很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.77,0:58:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,会这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.64,0:58:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我会这么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.62,0:58:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,学生时代呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.63,0:58:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是有过啦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.63,0:58:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,初体验的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.77,0:58:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候很流行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.77,0:58:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你是太妹吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.78,0:58:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.63,0:59:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.77,0:59:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不好的记忆呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.78,0:59:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,算是黑暗记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.78,0:59:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是唷
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.62,0:59:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这次的话
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.76,0:59:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,当作挑战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.77,0:59:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.62,1:00:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这样呀
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.64,1:00:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,身体时间是24岁
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.64,1:00:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,性交时间也是24岁
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.65,1:00:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是心灵上
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.65,1:00:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,回到学生时代
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.62,1:00:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他是你的男友
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.65,1:01:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好羞耻
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.76,1:01:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子互相看
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.77,1:01:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,再靠近一点
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.77,1:01:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好羞耻
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.78,1:01:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.62,1:01:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不好呼吸呀
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.63,1:01:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.77,1:02:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不要笑
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.64,1:02:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.65,1:02:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.65,1:02:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.63,1:03:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好羞耻-什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.77,1:03:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很羞耻
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.79,1:03:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,会想笑的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.65,1:03:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.63,1:04:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎样的?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.78,1:04:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这个吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.79,1:04:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很敏感吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.63,1:04:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子摸
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.78,1:04:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.79,1:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好羞耻
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.79,1:05:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.76,1:05:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.77,1:05:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.64,1:05:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯好
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.72,1:05:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,再亲啰
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.66,1:06:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要舔啰
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.71,1:06:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.69,1:06:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢这样舔吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.63,1:06:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很害羞呀?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.77,1:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.64,1:07:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这样呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.78,1:07:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,很羞耻呀?\N是的呀
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.63,1:07:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不要闻汗味
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.64,1:07:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧?\N可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.65,1:08:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这里可以吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.71,1:08:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这里好湿呀\N不要说出来啦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.65,1:08:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么?\N淫水
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.64,1:09:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很湿呢
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.65,1:09:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说啦
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.64,1:09:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.64,1:09:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.80,1:10:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,脫掉比较好
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.78,1:10:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.79,1:10:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,現在还遮住?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.66,1:12:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.67,1:12:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这样如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.78,1:13:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.64,1:13:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,温柔吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.80,1:13:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.67,1:13:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,很羞耻
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.67,1:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,还在害羞呀
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.66,1:15:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这样舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.66,1:16:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看吧\N不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.80,1:16:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,起来
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.65,1:16:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我脫吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.67,1:16:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这么生涩呀?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.67,1:16:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不是要当作第一次嘛?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.81,1:17:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始呢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.65,1:17:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.66,1:17:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.66,1:17:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.68,1:17:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.70,1:18:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不记得了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.67,1:18:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是唷
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.81,1:18:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可以脱掉吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.65,1:18:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,来舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.66,1:18:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可以舔吗?\N嗯，可以
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.70,1:18:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.82,1:19:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样?\N很有趣
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.66,1:19:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉很棒
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.68,1:19:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.67,1:19:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.82,1:20:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.66,1:20:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是唷
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.66,1:20:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀，不是很厉害嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.80,1:21:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子开始的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.81,1:21:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始不会很快
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.81,1:21:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是唷
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.66,1:21:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越刺激呢
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.70,1:21:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我要先习惯一下
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.67,1:21:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是唷
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.69,1:21:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,刚舔时会害羞呀?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.66,1:21:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.71,1:22:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要习慣一下
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.81,1:22:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是唷
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.68,1:22:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,过来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.82,1:22:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.82,1:22:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好羞耻
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.75,1:23:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的话
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.66,1:23:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.66,1:23:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,会好痒
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.76,1:24:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.80,1:24:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,很刺激吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.79,1:25:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很刺激
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.83,1:25:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.69,1:25:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很痒啊\N会痒呀
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.69,1:26:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.67,1:26:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,累了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.67,1:26:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.82,1:26:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.69,1:26:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,都会戴呀?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.73,1:26:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.75,1:27:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.68,1:27:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,很羞耻呢
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.69,1:27:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不一样呀?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.70,1:27:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.67,1:27:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这是綠色的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.68,1:27:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.82,1:27:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,背后插入吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.82,1:27:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,背后吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.83,1:27:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,很湿呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.81,1:28:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.84,1:28:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.69,1:28:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很痒
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.69,1:30:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这样舒服吧?\N嗯是的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.69,1:30:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.71,1:30:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这样插
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.69,1:31:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.69,1:34:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧?\N沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.70,1:34:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,换你在上面吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.84,1:34:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.80,1:35:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.85,1:35:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,常常做吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.68,1:35:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.83,1:35:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不行
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.85,1:35:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,过来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.70,1:36:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我动吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.70,1:36:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.70,1:37:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,脚张开让我看看
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.83,1:37:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.69,1:38:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.69,1:38:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很亲密
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.83,1:38:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢这样
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.80,1:39:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很痒呢
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.70,1:39:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,身体很敏感呢
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.70,1:39:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,很会玩弄我呀
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.71,1:39:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.70,1:39:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有过这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.70,1:39:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.70,1:39:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,只有跟我吗?\N 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.85,1:40:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.69,1:40:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.73,1:40:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.69,1:41:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.71,1:42:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.72,1:42:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有呀
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.71,1:43:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.74,1:43:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.71,1:43:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射吗?\N可以哦
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.73,1:45:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.70,1:45:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不能射里面啊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.85,1:45:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.72,1:45:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.73,1:45:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都这样吧
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.73,1:45:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沒关系 不用了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.71,1:45:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.71,1:46:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有点苦
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.79,1:46:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.73,1:46:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好好加油\N 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.73,1:46:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,想哭呀?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.73,1:46:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.73,1:46:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛都湿润了呀
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.84,1:46:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.72,1:47:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,性交如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.72,1:47:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要说呢?羞耻吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.73,1:47:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,感受上
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.73,1:47:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,比较没有爱情那种感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.70,1:47:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始很羞耻
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.71,1:47:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果用私底下的感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.75,1:47:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,都是这样的感觉呀?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.72,1:47:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.11,1:48:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都是
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.85,1:48:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.86,1:48:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不是大家都说的那种
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.86,1:48:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好难说
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.87,1:48:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一般的性交吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.71,1:48:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.85,1:48:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这4年的性交如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.85,1:48:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,确实呢
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.72,1:48:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经体验很多了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.71,1:49:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.85,1:49:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,跟鏡头说最后的话吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.86,1:49:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.87,1:49:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.78,1:49:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这时候差不多了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.85,1:49:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,也是沒办法呢
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.86,1:49:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,跟大家说说吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.86,1:50:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,想说什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.87,1:50:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,目前为止，真的很谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.74,1:50:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一直这样支持我
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.84,1:50:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,当然引退之后
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.72,1:50:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要说支持我也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.85,1:50:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.83,1:50:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还是希望能被支持
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.73,1:50:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,之后要开始新的生活
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.77,1:50:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.86,1:51:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是忘记啦
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.73,1:51:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.74,1:51:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,会怀念这样吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.71,1:51:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,能当AV女优很不错
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.85,1:51:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不是那么活泼的人
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.72,1:51:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,加上还是要适应
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.73,1:51:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的社会
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.87,1:51:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的工作也是要尝试
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.72,1:51:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,至少这边的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.85,1:52:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,已经很清楚了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.82,1:52:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,以后呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.86,1:52:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就是結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.87,1:52:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,当个家庭主妇这样的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.87,1:52:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很一般呢
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.88,1:52:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就是很女生的呀
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.78,1:52:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.72,1:52:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一般人的想法
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.74,1:52:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就是想走自己想走的路
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.74,1:52:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不错呀
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.77,1:53:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,明天回到一般的24岁
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.87,1:53:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.74,1:56:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,再見，时本杏